snippet.title: 200 Items Listed at the Same Prices on eBay, Poshmark, and Facebook Marketplace - What Happened?
snippet.description:
Where will things sell if they are listed at the same time at the same price on eBay, Poshmark, and Facebook Marketplace? That's what I wanted to find out. I listed over 200 items to the three platforms. In this video, I go over the 168 items that sold. Watch to find out which platform wins!

Watch these 3 videos to see each of the first 50+ sales in detail!
1) https://youtu.be/7-Ez4ZfkOBc
2) https://youtu.be/qOI4ZpYh06s
3) https://youtu.be/vWAOzTWwE6M

My email: amberresellsstuff@gmail.com
My Poshmark closet: DressedByAmber
My eBay store: DressedByAmber2

1:31 Facebook Marketplace

9:00 Poshmark
